         <div type="translation">
            <ab>[- - -] bishop [[Maximinus]] Dionysios [- - - not?] to be the(?) authorized bishop, but [- - -] to correct such disorder [- - -] the aforementioned when they realized that they &lt;OR: the aforementioned conspirators . . . themselves&gt; [- - -] (2nd hand) to return to us . . . [- - -] (1st hand) by putting on a pious face and hiding(?) their true intentions [- - -];Didymos who cons over Homer and perverts(?) Holy Writings, and even... (left unfinished)</ab>
